title: Effects of Rationing on Consumer Bahaviour in Chinese Urban Households.
author-name: Ding, H.
author-name: Hadri, K.
keywords: CONSUMPTION ; HOUSEHOLD ; ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT
length: 13 pages
abstract: This paper examines the consequences of housing rationing on the consumption behaviour of Chinese urban households in Jiangsu province during the years 1992-1993.
classification-jel: D12 O12
creation-date: 1999
handle: RePEc:exe:wpaper:9902

